response.overview: Enter a new world of respect, window and awe for one of the most amazing creations anywhere, as Emmy Award-Winner, Mick Kalber explores Halemaumau's current ash explosion and the spectacular Kamoamoa fissure eruption of 2011. This is literally the birth of the earth!  "Kilauea's Most Recent Eruptions" is an odyssey of sight and sound allowing us to go behind the scenes to observe, the world's most active volcano.
response.title: VolcanoScapes - Kilauea's Most Recent Eruption
